						               													<description>Mobile devices are unable to constrain Cut the Rope in digital form. The game managed to escape to the tabletop!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Little green monster Om Nom loves candy. But it is so hard to get it! Help him get the sweets by playing chains of cards. Don&amp;rsquo;t forget to use the scissors card at the right time. Be careful &amp;ndash; your opponents want to become the best friend of Om Nom too! To win, you will have to play smart and watch other players carefully.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the beginning of the game, each player gets a pile of numbered cards. The goal of each player is to get rid of all the cards from their pile. A top card from a player&amp;rsquo;s pile can be played to any one of three available &amp;ldquo;levels&amp;rdquo;. However, you can only play cards to form chains in &amp;ldquo;levels&amp;rdquo;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cards in chains have to go in ascending or descending order and no number can be skipped. Players also have a hand of cards. Cards from the hand can be used to form &amp;ldquo;supplies&amp;rdquo;. Cards from &amp;ldquo;supplies&amp;rdquo; can be played to &amp;ldquo;levels&amp;rdquo; as well. As soon as one player&amp;rsquo;s pile is empty, that player wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
